HEADWORD: Volante
<hw>Vo*lan"te</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Sp., prop.,
flying.]</ety> <def>A two-wheeled carriage formerly much used in Cuba.
The body is in front of the axle; the driver rides on the
horse.</def>⟦br⟧
